# scripts/refresh-project-fields-and-items.ps1
# Updates single-select field options with rich descriptions + brand colours on the
# LotusGift GitHub Project v2 (project #9, owner goldr0g3r).
#
# Usage:
#   .\scripts\refresh-project-fields-and-items.ps1
#
# Prerequisites:
#   - gh CLI installed + authenticated with `project` scope.
#   - Field IDs captured from `gh project field-list 9 --owner goldr0g3r`.
#
# This script:
#   1. Updates every single-select field's options with rich descriptions + colours.
#   2. The option IDs are regenerated by GitHub after the update.

